  if (event.origin === 'https://example.com') {
    console.log(event.data); // "Hello from tab 1!"
  }
});
```

### 2. **BroadcastChannel API**

The BroadcastChannel API is a simple way to send messages between windows, tabs, or workers. It's supported by most modern browsers.

```javascript
// In the first tab
